---
const title = 'Pagina nao encontrada';
const description = 'O conteudo que voce tentou abrir nao existe mais ou mudou de endereco.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title} - ShelfFlow Docs</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #fdfbf7;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
        --border: #e8e2d9;
        --text: #3d3529;
        --muted: #6b6054;
        --accent: #b37800;
        --accent-soft: #fff8e6;
        --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(61, 53, 41, 0.08);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255, 248, 230, 0.95), transparent 38%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #fdfbf7 0%, #f7f2ea 100%);
      }

      main {
        width: min(680px, 100%);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: var(--panel);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 1.25rem 0 0.75rem;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
        line-height: 0.98;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 54ch;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.875rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 46px;
        padding: 0 1rem;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition:
          transform 160ms ease,
          border-color 160ms ease,
          background-color 160ms ease,
          color 160ms ease,
          box-shadow 160ms ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .button-primary {
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #fdfbf7;
        box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(179, 120, 0, 0.18);
      }

      .button-primary:hover {
        background: #9c6900;
      }

      .button-secondary {
        border-color: var(--border);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .button-secondary:hover {
        border-color: #d7cdbd;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      }

      .meta {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="eyebrow">Erro 404</div>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
      <p>{description}</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/getting-started/">Ir para a documentacao</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="https://shelfflow.com.br/dashboard">Abrir dashboard</a>
      </div>
      <p class="meta">
        Se voce chegou aqui por um link antigo, o conteudo pode ter sido reorganizado para a nova estrutura da central de ajuda.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
